%package ncat
Summary: Nmap's Netcat replacement
Requires(post): %{_sbindir}/alternatives
Requires(preun): %{_sbindir}/alternatives
Obsoletes: nc < 1.109.20120711-2
Obsoletes: nc6 < 1.00-22
